➜医疗人员：将分析马拉多纳死前是否摄入违禁药物或酒精
http://www.sohu.com/a/434454749_260616	23409
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
